snippet.title: Diana playing with Baby Born Doll Videos for children
snippet.description:
A little girl is playing with dolls. These are Diana's favorite dolls - Baby Born. The girl cares for the dolls like her mother: feeds, bathes,  learn colors and puts them to bed. Learn colors together with us in this fun and educational video for #children and toddlers.
